step_data.thought: I've filled the search box with 'night vision goggles' and now I need to execute the search to see the results. This will allow me to find similar products to compare with the Nightfox Vulpes model I found earlier. The Nightfox Vulpes has specific features like an integrated laser rangefinder, 1080p sensor, video recording capability, 220yd range, 6x magnification, and is priced at $399.00 with a 5-star rating. By searching for general night vision goggles, I'll be able to see what other options are available and how they compare in terms of features and price.
